data.description: YOUR NEW home is located less than 10 miles from SUNSEEKER Resorts, downtown Punta Gorda and world class fishing that you can enjoy all year long! Welcome to 78 Lima Street in the desirable Deep Creek Community. Your NEW home is thoughtfully designed, and it offers 3 bedrooms, including a versatile office with the potential to serve as a 4th bedroom and 2 bathrooms, along with the convenience of a 2-car garage. Step outside and discover your private oasis, featuring an inviting inground pool enclosed by a screened lanai with a covered porch area. These outdoor spaces create an ideal setting for relaxation and outdoor gatherings. Inside, the office features stunning barn doors, seamlessly connecting it to the kitchen and dining area, offering versatility in its use. Imagine yourself in this newly updated kitchen! With newer appliances and plenty of room to work it's the perfect place to cook up your favorite dishes or try out new recipes. Whether it's a quiet weeknight dinner or a special gathering with loved ones, this kitchen WILL inspire your culinary creativity and make you feel right at home. With fresh interior paint and the added durability of LVP floors in the kitchen, dining room, and office, this home is move-in ready and awaits your personal touch. Additional recent and valuable updates include a newer water heater and a newer shingle roof, providing added peace of mind. 78 lima street is on an oversized corner lot, which provides  a generous outdoor space for various activities and potential future enhancements. Last but certainly not least your new home is close proximity to parks, golf courses, and shopping centers. Deep Creek provides residents with a balanced blend of nature and convenience, making it an ideal place to call home for those seeking a tranquil Florida lifestyle.
